<br />

<br />
He's exactly right.  A charmed pet takes a maximum of 1/3rd (33%) of the experience on kill (provided you do at least 1pt of damage to the mob).   From there is scales backward based on what percent of the total damage your pet does.. If your pet does 50% of the damage it takes 50% of 33% (16.5% or 1/6th) the experience.  So if your pet only does 1/3rd of the total damage to the mob being killed (because of its nerfed DPS) it will only take 1/3 of its maximum 33% of the exp.. so 1/9th or 11%.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
