I like to think of myself as an opportunistic class. When a pet presents itself I'm a dps class, when it doesn't I'm a CC/debuffing class. When there's no pets and nothing is mezzable and my group has a shaman I like to think of myself as the soon-to-be-canceling-my-account class. <img src="images/smiles/icon_evil.gif" alt="icon_evil.gif" border="0" /> 
